          '테니까 fits because the speaker\'s own volitional plan (I\'ll go ahead) grounds a request (take your time and follow). 텐데 expresses conjecture about uncontrollable facts, not the speaker\'s own intended action used as a basis for a command, so 을 텐데 is unnatural here.',
